apt-get update
apt-get install quilt libsdl1.2-dev libsdl-gfx1.2-dev libsdl-image1.2-dev libsdl-ttf2.0-dev libqt4-dev dh-make virtualbox-ose-guest-x11 libboost-dev libboost-thread-dev

extract source to pkgname-pkgver directory (BASEDIR)
within BASEDIR, run dh_make -f ../SOURCEARCHIVE

place all files from this folder (except this one) in BASEDIR/debian

for binary package:
dpkg-buildpackage

for source package suitable for ppa:
debuild -S -sa

to upload to ppa:
dput -f ppa:jakob-gruber/picmi ../picmi_1.2.0-2_source.changes
